videos.headline: Adkins swings pass to Huntley for 51-yard TD

videos.description: On a kickoff return, Jason Huntley catches and runs 87 yards for a touchdown to cut the Aggies' deficit to 21-14.
videos.headline: Huntley scores 87-yard TD on kickoff return
